Class ConfigMapConsumer

java.lang.Object
oracle.kubernetes.operator.helpers.ConfigMapConsumer
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.util.Map<java.lang.String,​java.lang.String>
Direct Known Subclasses:
TuningParametersImpl
public class ConfigMapConsumer
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Map<java.lang.String,​java.lang.String>
Kubernetes mounts ConfigMaps in the Pod's file-system as directories where the contained files are named with the keys and the contents of the file are the values. This class assists with parsing this data and representing it as a Map.
